<div class="page donate-page">
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="site-header__inner">
      <h1 class="site-title"><%= link_to "The Albion Online Data Project", root_path %></h1>
      <p class="site-tagline">Realtime market and gold data for Albion Online</p>
      <%= render "nav", current: :donate %>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="disclaimer banner">
    <p><strong>These tools are not affiliated with Albion Online or Sandbox Interactive GmbH.</strong></p>
  </div>

  <main class="main-content">
    <section class="content-section hero" id="support">
      <h2><a href="#support">Support the Albion Data Project</a></h2>
      <p class="lead">The Albion Data Project is free to use and run entirely on donations and Stanx/Paul's personal credit card 😅. If you find the data, API, or client useful, consider chipping in to help keep the servers running.</p>
      <p class="hero__cta">
        <a href="https://ko-fi.com/aodp2024" class="btn btn--primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Donate on Ko-fi</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section" id="costs">
      <h2><a href="#costs">Where Your Donation Goes</a></h2>
      <p>Every donation goes directly toward keeping the project online. The main recurring costs are:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Server</strong> — a Hetzner EX44 dedicated server, which runs the API, database, and data ingestion, costs <strong>€49/month</strong> (roughly €588/year).</li>
        <li><strong>Domain</strong> — the <code>.com</code> domain registration is renewed yearly, at roughly <strong>$12/year</strong>.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Donations of any size help cover these costs and keep the project sustainable for the whole community.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section" id="how">
      <h2><a href="#how">How to Donate</a></h2>
      <p>Donations are handled through Ko-fi, which supports one-time tips as well as recurring monthly support:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://ko-fi.com/aodp2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ko-fi.com/aodp2024</a> — one-time tip or monthly subscription, whichever works best for you.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Every tip and subscription is announced (amount only, no personal details) in our Discord, so you can see the support rolling in in real time.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section" id="privacy">
      <h2><a href="#privacy">Privacy &amp; the Supporter Role</a></h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Donations are <strong>public by default</strong> — but you can mark yours as private when submitting on Ko-fi if you'd rather not have it shown.</li>
        <li>Your <strong>real name is never exposed</strong>, regardless of your privacy setting. However, if you donate publicly, your <strong>Ko-fi username and message are shown</strong> on our Ko-fi page — please don't include personal or identifying details in your message.</li>
        <li>Want the Discord <strong>"Supporter" role</strong>? Ping <strong>Stanx</strong> in <strong>#General</strong> on Discord after donating and we'll add it for you. The role only changes the color of your username — there are <strong>no other perks</strong> tied to donating.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <p><%= link_to "The Albion Online Data Project", root_path %></p>
  </footer>
</div>
